## 13. Dynamic Rule Config

### Q: How do rules get updated without redeploying?

| Approach | How | Trade-off |
|----------|-----|-----------|
| **Pull (polling)** ✅ | Gateways poll config DB every 30s | Simple, 30s propagation delay |
| Push (ZooKeeper / pub-sub) | Config service pushes updates | Near-instant, complex |

Default to polling. Only use push for scenarios needing near-instant updates (active DDoS mitigation).

