## 16. Decision Cheat Sheet

| Layer | Decision |
|-------|----------|
| Placement | API Gateway |
| Client ID | User ID / IP / API Key, stacked; strictest wins |
| Algorithm | Token Bucket |
| Storage | Redis, sharded by client ID |
| Concurrency | Lua scripts (atomic read-compute-write) |
| Rejection | HTTP 429 + `X-RateLimit-*` headers, fail fast |
| Scale | Redis Cluster with ~10 shards |
| HA | Master-replica per shard + fail closed |
| Latency | Connection pooling + geo-distribution |
| Hot keys | Client SDK throttling + blocklist + DDoS shield |
| Dynamic config | Polling every 30s |

### Full Architecture

```
Users → Cloudflare (DDoS) → Regional Gateways → Regional Redis Cluster
                                                  (10 shards, master-replica)
```

